<div class="mlp-docs-section-heading"><i class="fas fa-star-and-crescent"></i> Term 1 — Halal Content Policy</div>
<p class="mlp-docs-lead">All content created, published, shared, or hosted through ptero.us.ci must strictly comply with Islamic Halal standards. This is a mandatory, non-negotiable condition of using our platform.</p>
