<li><strong>LocalStorage Wipes:</strong> Browser-based backups stored in LocalStorage can be erased by browser updates, clearing cache, or platform resets. We are not liable for any such loss.</li>
<li><strong>Server-Side Resets:</strong> During beta, the database may be wiped, migrated, or reset as part of development work. All shared links and AI cache may be permanently deleted.</li>
<li><strong>Your Responsibility:</strong> You are solely responsible for maintaining external copies of any code or content you create on ptero.eu.cc. Always save important work locally.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="mlp-docs-card" style="border-color:rgba(239,68,68,0.35);background:rgba(239,68,68,0.04);">
